name: Sustainability
description:
Kimil Tekstil is one of the leading home textile manufacturers and sustainability is its leading responsibility. One of the most important targets of Kimil Tekstil is applying all steps of sustainability with all its aspects including environment, society and economy within the company.

Ensuring the sustainability of its high-quality understanding, focusing on customer needs and being reliable both in its products and production processes are among Kimil Tekstil’s basic targets. Kimil Tekstil pays effort to fulfil and apply sustainability with full details in all its production and management processes from raw material to the final product.

Kimil Tekstil utilizes environmentally sensitive production processes which do not risk human health in its activities to contribute the economy for the sake of a clean future. Besides, adding value to its employees and the society is one of the most important principles of Kimil Tekstil with its conscious about its responsibilities.

Kimil Tekstil is proud of its Oeko-Tex® Step certification and using Made in Green label on its products. Kimil Tekstil can make production for its customers who ask for organic products with its GOTS certificate as well.

Moreover, Kimil Tekstil can provide high level products and services with the BSCI document for social responsibility and environmental health and occupational safety.

name: Education & Health
description:
Kimil Tekstil, besides its manufacturer identity, conducts various 
social responsibility activities that will contribute the society, 
especially in education and health in Denizli and Güney district of 
Denizli, where the roots of the founder family lie. Kimil Tekstil aims 
at contributing the social aspect of sustainability
